data.description: Beautiful move in ready condo tucked near a wooded area. Lake privilege  access to Voorheis Lake, an all sports lake with beach & boat launch. Soak up the sun water skiing, paddle boarding, kayaking, & jet skiing. This condo features a spacious living room with newer laminate flooring. Kitchen with an ample amount of solid oak cupboards, newer laminate flooring, dishwasher, & new fridge, new stove, & new microwave. Updated full bathroom. Very large primary bedroom with new carpet & a walk in closet. Nice size second bedroom with new carpet. Attached garage w/ electric opener. Newer vinyl windows, newer HWT, updated light fixtures throughout, new carpet, fresh paint throughout, new doors/closet doors throughout, new blinds, new door hardware, new thermostat, new nest smoke detectors, new washer/dryer, & much more. All appliances included. Water/sewer, garbage, snow, & grass included in HOA fee. Close to shopping, dining, & freeways. Don't miss out, schedule your showing today!
